.DT
mailinfo
Discworld player help
mailinfo

Name
.SI 5
mailinfo - mail status of a player.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
mailinfo [name]
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Mailinfo returns the mail status of a player, without having to type finger
and find it in there. Will return total number of mail messages and the number
that are unread. If [name] is ommited, then it returns your own mail status.
.EP

Examples :
.SI 5
> mailinfo chrisy
Player Chrisy: 75 mail messages.
> mailinfo
Player Chrisy: 75 mail messages.
> mailinfo pinkfish
Player Pinkfish: 122 mail messages, 3 of them unread.
.EI

See also
.SI 5
finger, mailer
.EI
